name: LianjaX-VFP Importers
body:
### Welcome to LianjaX Visual FoxPro File Importers
This LianjaX repository contains the Lianja scripts (.prg files) used to import Visual FoxPro files into Lianja. These are also included in the Lianja App Builder distribution and are located in the Lianja library folder.

All software contained here is licensed under the Apache 2 OSS license.
